OL,3,CFire boss suspended over historical
OL,4,Csocial media posts
OL,6,FThe Deputy Chief at North Wales Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service has been suspended
OL,8,Fover a historical social media post.
OL,10,FThe Service suspended DCFO Stewart
OL,11,FForshaw on Friday night after an
OL,12,Fallegedly homophobic Twitter/X post
OL,13,Ffrom 2012 came to light.
OL,15,FMr Forshaw is responsible for
OL,16,FEquality, Diversity and Inclusivity at
OL,17,Fthe service and recieved an award on
OL,18,Fbehalf of the service for Outstanding
OL,19,FContribution in Public Services by
OL,20,FPride Cymru in 2024.
