OL,6,FIn a statement to staff seen by ITV
OL,7,FWales, Chief Fire Officer Dawn Docx
OL,8,Fsaid, "I took the precautionary step
OL,9,Fof suspending the Deputy while a full
OL,10,Fand fair investigation takes place.
OL,12,F"I want to provide reassurance that I
OL,13,Fam fully committed to upholding the
OL,14,Fhighest standards of professionalism,
OL,15,Fintegrity, and trust in our Service."
OL,17,FIt comes as ITV News understands a
OL,18,Flong-awaited cultural review into the
OL,19,Ftroubled fire service is set to be
OL,20,Fpublished on Wednesday, 5 February.
