OL,6,FThe review was announced by the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment after more than 35
OL,8,Fwhistleblowers contacted ITV News
OL,9,Fdescribing a "toxic culture" at North
OL,10,FWales Fire and Rescue Service.
OL,12,FMid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService are also due to publish a
OL,14,Freview into its culture.
OL,16,FThe Fire Brigades Union said, "Members
OL,17,Fare shocked, alarmed and appalled at
OL,18,Fthese recent developments.
